#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The module <guilabel>CDDB Retrieval</guilabel> is divided in the "
"<guilabel>Lookup</guilabel> tab and the <guilabel>Submit</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Modul <guilabel>Pridobivanje CDDB</guilabel> je razdeljen na zavihek "
"<guilabel>Iskanje</guilabel> in zavihek <guilabel>Pošlji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Lookup Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Iskanje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The <guilabel>Lookup</guilabel> tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zavihek <guilabel>Iskanje</guilabel></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The <guilabel>Lookup</guilabel> tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihek <guilabel>Iskanje</guilabel></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Lookup</guilabel> tab sets up the <acronym>CDDB</acronym> "
"functions of &kde;."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Iskanje</guilabel> nastavi funkcije <acronym>CDDB</"
"acronym> &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the options <guilabel>Enable MusicBrainz lookup</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Enable freedb lookup</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko možnosti <guilabel>Omogoči iskanje MusicBrainz</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Omogoči iskanje freedb</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Freedb server</guilabel> section determines which CDDB mirror "
"site is used by &kde; to get album information. You can enter a server name, "
"port number and protocol using the text boxes and drop down boxes or you can "
"click the <guibutton>Show Mirror List</guibutton> button. Clicking this "
"button will open a new window with a list of CDDB mirrors and their "
"locations. Simply select the server you want from the list and click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>Strežnik Freedb</guilabel> določa, katero zrcalno mesto "
"CDDB uporablja &kde; da dobite informacije o albumu. Ime strežnika, številko "
"vrat in protokol lahko vnesete z uporabo besedilnih polj in spustnih polj "
"ali pa kliknete gumb <guibutton>Pokaži seznam zrcalnih strežnikov</"
"guibutton>. S klikom na ta gumb se odpre novo okno s seznamom zrcalnih "
"strežnikov CDDB in njihovimi lokacijami. Na seznamu preprosto izberite "
"želeni strežnik in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The section labeled <guilabel>Cache Locations</guilabel> lets you determine "
"where the CDDB information is saved on your computer. To add a folder, enter "
"the folder location in the text box at the top of the section and click "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton>. You can also select a folder by clicking on the "
"blue file folder to the right of the text box. To delete a folder, click on "
"the folder name once with the &LMB; and click <guibutton>Remove</guibutton>. "
"You can change the order the folders are searched by clicking on the folder "
"name and clicking on the <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and <guibutton>Move "
"Down</guibutton> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek z oznako <guilabel>Lokacije predpomnilnika</guilabel> vam omogoča, "
"da določite, kje so shranjene informacije CDDB v vašem računalniku. Če "
"želite dodati mapo, vnesite lokacijo mape v besedilno polje na vrhu razdelka "
"in kliknite <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Mapo lahko izberete tudi tako, da "
"kliknete modro mapo z datotekami na desni strani besedilnega polja. Za "
"brisanje mape enkrat kliknite na ime mape z &LMB; in kliknite "
"<guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>. Vrstni red iskanja po mapah lahko "
"spremenite tako, da kliknete ime mape in kliknete gumba <guibutton>Premakni "
"navzgor</guibutton> in <guibutton>Premakni dol</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Help</guibutton> button opens the this help contents page. "
"The <guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button restores the default values of "
"all entries in this dialog; <guibutton>OK</guibutton> saves the current "
"settings and exits; <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> saves the current settings "
"without exiting."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton> odpre stran z vsebino te pomoči. Gumb "
"<guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton> obnovi privzete vrednosti vseh vnosov v tem "
"pogovornem oknu; <guibutton>OK</guibutton> shrani trenutne nastavitve in "
"zapre; <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton> shrani trenutne nastavitve brez izhoda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Submit Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pošlji"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Submit tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Pošlji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Submit</guilabel> tab sets up connection to a mail server or a "
"web server to submit new <acronym>CDDB</acronym> entries. This is useful if "
"you do not have your own system configured as a server."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Pošlji</guilabel> nastavi povezavo s poštnim ali spletnim "
"strežnikom za oddajo novih <acronym>CDDB</acronym> vnosov. To je uporabno, "
"če nimate lastnega sistema konfiguriranega kot strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you plan to submit a CDDB entry, enter your email address into the first "
"textbox."
msgstr ""
"Če nameravate oddati vnos CDDB, vnesite svoj e-poštni naslov v prvo "
"besedilno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter a server name or port number in the text boxes provided. If "
"you want to send this information to the international servers, you do not "
"need to change anything."
msgstr ""
"V ponujena besedilna polja lahko vnesete ime strežnika ali številko vrat. Če "
"želite te podatke poslati mednarodnim strežnikom, vam ni treba ničesar "
"spremeniti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "The CD Database Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik podatkovnih baz CD-jev"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &CD; Database Editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Program &CD; Urejevalnik baze podatkov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &CD; Database Editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&CD; Urejevalnik baze podatkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &CD; Database Editor allows you to modify, download, save, annotate, and "
"upload <link linkend=\"cddb-support\"><acronym>CDDB</acronym> (Compact Disc "
"Data Base)</link> entries."
msgstr ""
"&CD; Urejevalnik zbirke podatkov vam omogoča spreminjanje, prenos, "
"shranjevanje, komentiranje in nalaganje vnosov <link linkend=\"cddb-support"
"\"><acronym>CDDB</acronym> (Baza podatkov zgoščenk)</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is an entry in your local <acronym>CDDB</acronym> tree (see the "
"<link linkend=\"cddb-page\">CDDB subsection</link> in the Configuration "
"chapter) for the &CD; in your &CD-ROM; drive, or if the disc could be found "
"in the freedb, you will see the name of the artist and the title of the &CD; "
"in the <guilabel>Artist:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Title</guilabel> fields "
"and a list of tracks with song titles in the <interface>Tracks</interface> "
"selection box. Otherwise, you will see a list of tracks and play times "
"without titles."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja vnos v vašem lokalnem drevesu <acronym>CDDB</acronym> (glejte "
"<link linkend=\"cddb-page\">podrazdelek CDDB</link> v poglavju "
"Konfiguracija) za &CD; v vašem &CD-ROM; ali če je disk mogoče najti v "
"freedb, boste videli ime izvajalca in naslov &CD; v poljih "
"<guilabel>Izvajalec:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Naslov</guilabel> ter seznam "
"skladb z naslovi pesmi v izbirnem polju <interface>Skladbe</interface>. V "
"nasprotnem primeru boste videli seznam skladb in čase predvajanja brez "
"naslovov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make an annotation for the entire disc with the <guilabel>Comment</"
"guilabel> field under the <guilabel>Title</guilabel> field, or for a "
"selected track in the <guilabel>Tracks</guilabel> selection box with the "
"adjacent <guibutton>Comment</guibutton> button. If you select a track in the "
"<guilabel>Tracks</guilabel> selection box, the title, if present, will "
"appear in the <guilabel>Title</guilabel> field below. You can type a title "
"for the track in the box, or edit the entry to suit your needs. Press the "
"<keycap>Return</keycap> key on your keyboard, and the text will appear in "
"the proper line in the selection box."
msgstr ""
"Opombo lahko naredite za celoten disk s poljem <guilabel>Komentar</guilabel> "
"pod poljem <guilabel>Naslov</guilabel> ali za izbrano skladbo v izbirnem "
"polju <guilabel>Skladbe</guilabel> z sosednji gumb <guibutton>Komentar</"
"guibutton>. Če izberete skladbo v izbirnem polju <guilabel>Skladbe</"
"guilabel>, bo naslov, če obstaja, prikazan v spodnjem polju "
"<guilabel>Naslov</guilabel>. V polje lahko vnesete naslov skladbe ali "
"uredite vnos, da bo ustrezal vašim potrebam. Pritisnite tipko "
"<keycap>Return</keycap> na tipkovnici in besedilo se bo pojavilo v ustrezni "
"vrstici v izbirnem polju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once all tracks have been given titles and the <guilabel>Artist:</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Title</guilabel> fields have been filled out, you can press "
"the <guibutton>Upload</guibutton> button to send your submission by email to "
"freedb."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse skladbe naslovljene in sta izpolnjeni polji <guilabel>Izvajalec:</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Naslov</guilabel>, lahko pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>Naloži</guibutton>, da pošljete svoj prispevek po elektronski "
"pošti na freedb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will be prompted to select a category for the submission. The "
"<guilabel>Disc ID</guilabel> section displays the 32 bit <acronym>ID</"
"acronym> code used by freedb to identify a compact disc. Above the "
"<acronym>ID</acronym> code is the category of the <guilabel>freedb</"
"guilabel> entry. These categories correspond to the subfolders tree of the "
"folder chosen in the <guilabel>freedb Base Folder:</guilabel> in the <link "
"linkend=\"cddb-page\"><guilabel>CDDB</guilabel> page</link> of the "
"configuration window."
msgstr ""
"Pozvani boste, da izberete kategorijo za oddajo. Razdelek <guilabel>ID "
"plošče</guilabel> prikazuje 32-bitno kodo <acronym>ID</acronym>, ki jo "
"uporablja freedb za identifikacijo zgoščenke. Nad kodo <acronym>ID</acronym> "
"je kategorija vnosa <guilabel>freedb</guilabel>. Te kategorije ustrezajo "
"drevesu podmap mape, izbrane v <guilabel>osnovni mapi freedb:</guilabel> na "
"strani <link linkend=\"cddb-page\"><guilabel>CDDB</guilabel></link> "
"konfiguracijsko okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Length:</guilabel> display shows the total play time of the "
"&CD;."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon <guilabel>Dolžina:</guilabel> prikazuje skupni čas predvajanja &CD;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Fetch Info</guibutton> button to download "
"<acronym>CDDB</acronym> data. Press the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button to "
"save your changes locally. The <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> button closes "
"the &CD; Database Editor without saving."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Pridobi informacije</guibutton>, da prenesete "
"podatke <acronym>CDDB</acronym>. Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>, da lokalno shranite spremembe. Gumb <guibutton>Prekliči</"
"guibutton> zapre &CD; Urejevalnik podatkovnih baz brez shranjevanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "<acronym>CDDB</acronym> Support"
msgstr "<acronym>CDDB</acronym> Podpora"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"freedb is a distributed network database accessible over the Internet that "
"contains information about most audio &CD;s in circulation. If you have "
"Internet access, you will likely never have to manually enter track "
"information for your &CD;s if you have this set up properly. See <link "
"linkend=\"cddb-page\">The CDDB Page</link> section for detailed instructions "
"on how to configure this service, and the <link linkend=\"cddb-editor\">&CD; "
"Database Editor</link> section for instructions on how to edit "
"<acronym>CDDB</acronym> entries."
msgstr ""
"freedb je porazdeljena omrežna zbirka podatkov, dostopna prek interneta, ki "
"vsebuje informacije o večini zvočnih CD-jev v obtoku. Če imate dostop do "
"interneta, vam verjetno nikoli ne bo treba ročno vnašati informacij o "
"skladbah za vaše CD-je, če ste to pravilno nastavili. Glejte razdelek <link "
"linkend=\"cddb-page\">Stran CDDB</link> za podrobna navodila o tem, kako "
"konfigurirati to storitev, in <link linkend=\"cddb-editor\">&CD; Razdelek "
"urejevalnika baze podatkov</link> za navodila o urejanju vnosov "
"<acronym>CDDB</acronym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use of the <acronym>CDDB</acronym> is free. Submissions from users are "
"encouraged."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba <acronym>CDDB</acronym> je brezplačna. Spodbujamo prispevke "
"uporabnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When preparing entries for the <acronym>CDDB</acronym>, please keep the "
"following points in mind:"
msgstr ""
"Ko pripravljate vnose za <acronym>CDDB</acronym>, upoštevajte naslednje "
"točke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <quote>standard</quote> latin characters in the entries. Some special "
"characters are supported, but Cyrillic or Greek alphabet submissions, for "
"example, cannot be accepted."
msgstr ""
"V vnosih uporabljajte <quote>standardne</quote> latinične znake. Nekateri "
"posebni znaki so podprti, vendar na primer vnos cirilice ali grške abecede "
"ni mogoč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use only one <keysym>/</keysym> character in the <guilabel>Disc Artist / "
"Title</guilabel> field in the &CD; Database Editor."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite samo en znak <keysym>/</keysym> v polju <guilabel>Izvajalec/naslov "
"plošče</guilabel> v polju &CD; Urejevalnik podatkovnih baz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For classical &CD;s, it is standard practice to put the composer's name in "
"the Artist section (before the slash) and the performer's name in the Title "
"section (after the slash)."
msgstr ""
"Pri klasičnih &CD;-jih je običajna praksa, da ime skladatelja postavite v "
"razdelek Izvajalec (pred poševnico) in ime izvajalca v razdelek Naslov (za "
"poševnico)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you send an entry that already exists in the database, any additional "
"information you provide may be added to the existing entry."
msgstr ""
"Če pošljete vnos, ki že obstaja v bazi podatkov, se morebitne dodatne "
"informacije, ki jih posredujete, lahko dodajo obstoječemu vnosu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the standard <acronym>CDDB</acronym> categories are installed in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.cddb</filename>. You can create as many "
"category subfolders as you like. However, when uploading, only the official "
"<acronym>CDDB</acronym> categories are displayed. The default upload address "
"is <email>gnudb-submit@gnudb.org</email>. For more information about "
"<abbrev>gnudb</abbrev> visit the <abbrev>gnudb</abbrev> homepage."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so standardne kategorije <acronym>CDDB</acronym> nameščene v "
"<filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.cddb</filename>. Ustvarite lahko "
"poljubno število podmap kategorij. Vendar pa so pri nalaganju prikazane samo "
"uradne kategorije <acronym>CDDB</acronym>. Privzeti naslov za nalaganje je "
"<email>gnudb-submit@gnudb.org</email>. Za več informacij o <abbrev>gnudb</"
"abbrev> obiščite domačo stran <abbrev>gnudb</abbrev>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The local <acronym>CDDB</acronym> entry for a particular &CD; is stored in "
"the file <filename><replaceable>category name</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>disc ID</replaceable></filename> under the <acronym>CDDB</"
"acronym> Base Folder. These files can be edited with any text editor."
msgstr ""
"Lokalni vnos <acronym>CDDB</acronym> za določen &CD; je shranjen v datoteki "
"<filename><replaceable>ime kategorije</replaceable>/<replaceable>ID diska</"
"replaceable></filename> pod osnovno mapo <acronym>CDDB</acronym>. Te "
